### PART 5: ANIMATION DETAILS

**Framer Motion animations used:**

| Element | Animation | Spec |
|---------|-----------|------|
| Main opinion card | Fade in + slide up | `initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}`, `animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}`, duration 0.3s |
| Each reply card | Staggered fade in | `initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 8 }}`, delay `index * 0.03` |
| Submit/Cancel buttons | Height expand | `initial={{ opacity: 0, height: 0 }}` to `animate={{ opacity: 1, height: 'auto' }}` |
| Nested reply expansion | Fade | `initial={{ opacity: 0 }}` to `animate={{ opacity: 1 }}` |
| Thread line on hover | Color transition | CSS `transition: background-color 0.2s ease` |
| All buttons | Scale on active | CSS `transform: scale(0.97)` on `:active` |
| Reply input focus | Border color | CSS `transition: border-color 0.2s ease` |
| Username hover | Color + underline | CSS `transition: color 0.15s ease` |

